an]]'' (born in [[Port Huron, Michigan|Port Huron]]) * [[Karen Ziemba]], [[Tony Award]]-winning stage actress, singer, and dancer (born in [[St. Joseph, Michigan|St. Joseph]]) * [[Kim Zimmer]], actress, ''[[Guiding Light]]'' (born in [[Grand Rapids, Michigan|Grand Rapids]]) {{colend}}
